These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
City: london, prague
There are 2 different favourite colors: apricot, aquamarine
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, mexican
The people have 2 different hobbies: video-games, drawing
1. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
2. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| City      | prague      | london    |
| Color           | aquamarine | apricot |
| Nationality   | italian       | mexican  |
| Hobby     | video-games      | drawing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: cauliflower, watermelon
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, april
There are 2 different nationalities: pakistani, mexican
City: san-francisco, nizza
1. the pakistani is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3
2. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Food          | watermelon | cauliflower |
| Birthday   | december       | april         |
| Nationality           | mexican     | pakistani         |
| City     | nizza    | san-francisco    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: parkour, biathlon
2 different pets are kept: fish, ferret
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, r&b
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: western, zombie
1. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Sport         | biathlon          | parkour |
| Pet           | ferret | fish     |
| Music-Genre   | folk            | r&b         |
| Movie-Genre     | zombie         | western   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, tea
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, airplane
The people have 2 different jobs:  security-guard, freelancer
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, cooking
1. the security-guard is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
2. the person drinking tea is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Beverage      | tea     | cola   |
| Transport   | airplane    | car |
| Job   | security-guard   | freelancer |
| Hobby           | dancing | cooking    |

