The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: azalea, aconite
1. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the dutch##3
3. the dutch is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Sport          | tennis    | biathlon     |
| Nationality   | dutch       | british |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | bird      |
| Flower     | aconite        | azalea |

