.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
2 different pets are kept: goat, mouse
There are 2 different favourite colors: purple, ebony
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, baccarat
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, taxi
1. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the person who likes purple is the alhambra-smoker##1
3. the alhambra-smoker is the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Pet      | mouse     | goat |
| Color          | ebony   | purple |
| Cigar   | baccarat     | alhambra     |
| Transport     | airplane | taxi     |

 